skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: saga quotes
des:
A Star Wars skill for Star Wars fans. Relive the best moments from the epic saga with this skill!
You will hear all the best, epic lines from the Star Wars universe. Just say the magic words and you can hear Yoda, Han Solo, Darth Vader, and many more answering.
I would say try this skill, but we know that: Do or do not. There is no try!

This is an unofficial Star Wars skill, I am not associated with Star Wars, Lucasfilm, or Disney in any way.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
